Why do you rar a tv show?  Why do you rar anything?  The compression is negligible and it's more of an annoyance when you're dealing with a network drive, i.e. NAS storage drive.  

It reminds me of a noob friend of mine that has to use every kind of security on his laptop with nothing on it... because it's there.

Dont complaint either you take it or you leave it alone.

thanks for the upload, i think i will enjoy this episode :)

i love the show.
